.IP "\fBuser\-setup\fR" 4
adds an live user account.
.IP "\fBsudo\fR" 4
grants sudo privileges to the live user.
.IP "\fBlocales\fR" 4
configures locales.
.IP "\fBtzdata\fR" 4
configures /etc/timezone.
.IP "\fBgdm\fR" 4
