configures autologin in kdm.
.IP "\fBlxdm\fR" 4
configures autologin in lxdm.
.IP "\fBnodm\fR" 4
configures autologin in nodm.
.IP "\fBslim\fR" 4
configures autologin in slim.
.IP "\fBxinit\fR" 4
